      "label": "Content description",
      "value": "Recto: The sender mentions riding or working animals (l. 4) and he asks the addressee to send him what he owes him (l. 7). He refers to a certain Ab\u016b al-Waf\u0101' who brought him something and he writes that he has written a letter to a third person with the addressee's information (l. 10) and that he has sent him a 'reliable' messenger (l. 11).\n\u00a0\nVerso: The beginning of a letter is three times repeated with the common opening formulae (ll. 2, 4, 6)"
    },
